CROCKER v. OAKES et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 8, 1903.) No. 185. Appeal from the Circuit Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. H. Y. M. Dennis, Jr., for appellants. Wm. T. Reed, for appellee.

Before WALLACE, TOWNSEND, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed in open court. See 117 Fed. 363.
